Conclusion
You have successfully completed an advanced adversary infrastructure investigation using Amass and Shodan. This lab demonstrated how to:

Enumerate domains using OSINT techniques with Amass
Gather intelligence on exposed systems using Shodan API
Correlate data from multiple sources to build comprehensive infrastructure maps
